OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSchool Afro-hair bans      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fprobably illegal - watchdog
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Children with Afro-textured hair should
OL,6, not be prevented from wearing natural  
OL,7, hairstyles at school, new guidance from
OL,8, Britain's human-rights watchdog says.  
OL,10,FSchool bans on hairstyles such as      
OL,11,Fbraids and cornrows are likely to be   
OL,12,Funlawful if they do not give exemptions
OL,13,Fon racial grounds, the Equality and    
OL,14,FHuman Rights Commission (EHRC) says.   
OL,16,FThe guidance will not affect government
OL,17,Fpolicy, but is intended to help stop   
OL,18,Fhair-based discrimination in schools.  
OL,20,FMinisters say they have issued advice. 
